Amerikanska PMI-siffror steg i oktober – Wall Street lyfter ytterligare
ISM inköpschefsindex för industrin steg till 48,3 i oktober jämfört med 47,8 i september, enligt Reuters.
01 Nov 2019, 13:48 by Nyhetsbyrån Direkt

US PMI figures rose in October - Wall Street lifts further
The ISM purchasing head index for the industry rose to 48.3 in October compared to 47.8 in September, according to Reuters.
01 Nov 2019, 13:48 by News Agency Direct
